text: The H700 Shenzhen Tower is a proposed megatall skyscraper in Shenzhen, China. It is planned to be tall with 110 floors. If built, the tower would become China's tallest building upon completion. The tower is designed by Chicago based company bKL Architecture. ==See also== *List of future tallest buildings in the world *Bionic Tower *Wuhan Greenland Center *Qianhai Tower *Wuhan CTF Centre *Shanghai Tower *Shanghai World Financial Center *KK100 *Ping An Finance Centre ==References== Category:Proposed buildings and structures in China Category:Buildings and structures in Shenzhen
